description:
4/3- Today on the show we had Jason Lee from gossip site "Hollywood Unlocked"  stop, and spilled all the tea about how he got started, breaking news, Jussie Smollett and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man that choked grocery store cashier for crushing his bag of chips and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
